{"tid":1820820,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[做任用] Twitter bot黑暗兵法","createTime":"2020-01-11T18:04:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-26T08:03:52.000Z","uid":11329,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"bda97c43d1f3aaf73c45a968e5124ba4c2967ded","tid":1820820,"uid":11329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T18:04:58.000Z","msg":"首先多謝#黃島獨手足既教學，咁好用既方法當然要話比大家聽<br />\n做左任幾個月，Twitter bot最麻煩既就係要逐條link禁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家有個方法係可以<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">一次過禁哂D link出黎</span></strong></span><br />\n咁做任就快好多啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<em><span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">以下呢個方法只係for電腦版同埋電腦配置ok既手足用，<br />\n否則支爆link果陣可能會搞到你部機好lag</span></span></em><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">1. 裝telegram電腦版（唔可以用網頁版）</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">2. 裝 OpenList Chrome Extension</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/openlist/nkpjembldfckmdchbdiclhfedcngbgnl?hl=en\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fopenlist%2Fnkpjembldfckmdchbdiclhfedcngbgnl%3Fhl%3Den&d=E2fLMnMY5FLAMirJUdBaWexpY9ERoCMedVnvBBvIoB8%3D&h=1485924d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/openlist/nkpjembldfckmdchbdiclhfedcngbgnl?hl=en</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">3. 抄Telegram信息</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/gzoiysp.png\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">4. 搵個website自動filter URL</span></strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.text-filter.com/Extract-Url-From-Text-Email-List-Leads.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.text-filter.com%2FExtract-Url-From-Text-Email-List-Leads.htm&d=E2fLMnMY5FLAMirJUdBaWexpY9ERoCMedVnvBBvIoB8%3D&h=fe72021f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.text-filter.com/Extract-Url-From-Text-Email-List-Leads.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">5. 然後抄URL list 上 clipboard</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/nEdKt1y.png\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">6. 按 OpenList Button, 將 URL Paste 落去噤 Open</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/WpinfHk.png\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">係copy堆link既時候最尾佢會醒多個關括號比你，<br />\ndel左佢，否則有一個網會死link<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BxPcjnf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBxPcjnf.png&h=d9aeedf5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">7. 然後支爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/Uxqpt3y.png\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>Twitter要人</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69445d13f4f59c8592b40f0a98c46b781ba59681","tid":1820820,"uid":11329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T18:06:40.000Z","msg":"每日pm @TwitterHelpBot 打 /task 拎任務"},{"pid":"a0865b7d6dbb7fb5ad1065bc98db232746b0c69a","tid":1820820,"uid":2662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"202